{%- comment -%} ════════════════════════════════════════════════
     PHOTO LIGHTBOX — outside .bfc4 (overflow:clip was clipping the close X)
     Used by hero slider + Shot On gallery via bfc4OpenHeroLightbox/bfc4OpenShotLightbox
     ════════════════════════════════════════════════ {%- endcomment -%}
<div class="ba-lightbox" id="ba-lightbox" onclick="bfc4LightboxClose(event)">
  <div class="ba-lightbox-inner">
